(143, 'student', '1st', '', 'Optimizing Library Usage Tracking at EARIST with Near Field Communication: Assessing Efficiency in Time Tracking and Record Accessibility', 'Efficient tracking of library usage is essential for managing resources, understanding student behavior, and improving service delivery. This study, “Optimizing Library Usage Tracking at EARIST with Near Field Communication (NFC),” introduces an NFC-based system to automate library check-ins, check-outs, and usage monitoring. By integrating NFC technology with a digital database, the system enables real-time recording of student activity, reduces manual errors, and ensures faster access to records. Experimental evaluation indicates enhanced accuracy, reduced processing time, and improved accessibility of usage data for both library staff and students, supporting more informed decision-making and resource management.', 'The NFC-based library tracking system demonstrates a significant improvement in the efficiency and accuracy of monitoring library usage at EARIST. By automating time tracking and record management, the system minimizes manual errors, reduces administrative workload, and provides instant access to usage data. Future enhancements may include mobile app integration, advanced analytics for usage trends, and personalized recommendations for students based on reading habits. Overall, this project contributes to smarter library management, better resource allocation, and enhanced student experience.', 'Kenneth Gabas ', '[\"Rada\",\"Matias\",\"Padon\",\"Obina\"]', 2, 23, '[4]', '[\"Quality Education\"]', '{\"0\":0,\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":1,\"4\":0,\"5\":0,\"6\":0,\"7\":0,\"8\":0,\"9\":0,\"10\":0,\"11\":0,\"12\":0,\"13\":0,\"14\":0,\"15\":0,\"16\":0}', 'completed', '2025-11-11 05:27:00', 44, 2023),
(144, 'student', '1st', '', 'Tarsie: Interactive Tagalog Animated E-Learning App for Pre-School Students', 'Early childhood education benefits greatly from engaging and interactive learning tools that foster language and cognitive development. Tarsie is an interactive Tagalog animated e-learning application designed for pre-school students to enhance language skills, literacy, and foundational knowledge through gamified lessons and storytelling. The app features animated characters, quizzes, and interactive exercises that encourage active participation while teaching basic vocabulary, numbers, and social concepts. Initial testing with young learners indicates improved engagement, better retention of lessons, and positive feedback from both students and educators.', 'Tarsie provides an innovative approach to early childhood education by combining animation, interactivity, and culturally relevant content in Tagalog. The application enhances learning engagement, supports language development, and prepares students for foundational academic skills in a fun and accessible way. Future improvements may include expanding content, integrating adaptive learning paths, and providing parental or teacher dashboards to track progress. Overall, Tarsie contributes to quality early education, promoting cognitive development and fostering a love for learning among young learners.', 'Joevelyn Fajardo ', '[\"Ornopia, Luigi\",\"Ayop, Mary Grace\",\"Javonillo, Alyssa Mae\",\"Efres, Curie Gayle\"]', 2, 23, '[4]', '[\"Quality Education\"]', '{\"0\":0,\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":1,\"4\":0,\"5\":0,\"6\":0,\"7\":0,\"8\":0,\"9\":0,\"10\":0,\"11\":0,\"12\":0,\"13\":0,\"14\":0,\"15\":0,\"16\":0}', 'completed', '2025-11-11 05:28:32', 44, 2023),
(145, 'student', '1st', '', 'Online Academic Performance Monitoring System for Eulogio Rodriguez Vocational High Schoo', 'Monitoring student academic performance is essential for identifying learning gaps, improving teaching strategies, and supporting student success. This study, “Online Academic Performance Monitoring System for Eulogio Rodriguez Vocational High School,” presents a web-based platform designed to track, manage, and analyze student performance in real-time. The system allows teachers to input grades, generate performance reports, and monitor progress, while students and parents can access dashboards to review academic standing and attendance. Initial testing shows that the platform reduces manual record-keeping, provides timely performance insights, and enhances communication among teachers, students, and parents.', 'The online academic performance monitoring system improves the efficiency and accuracy of tracking student performance at Eulogio Rodriguez Vocational High School. By providing real-time access to grades, attendance, and progress reports, the platform supports informed decision-making for teachers, empowers students to take responsibility for their learning, and enhances parental engagement. Future developments may include predictive analytics for academic performance, mobile app integration, and personalized learning recommendations. Overall, this system contributes to better educational outcomes and a more effective, transparent academic management process.', 'Merlita Latip', '[\"Vicente\",\"Lenchico\",\"Dee\",\"Millano\"]', 2, 23, '4', '\"Quality Education\"', '{\"0\":0.006799164228141308,\"1\":0.025519616901874542,\"2\":0.0022528001572936773,\"3\":0.7162949442863464,\"4\":0.0018133168341591954,\"5\":0.0010116816265508533,\"6\":0.0007037973264232278,\"7\":0.010785437189042568,\"8\":0.2133619487285614,\"9\":0.002285633236169815,\"10\":0.008666548877954483,\"11\":0.0006558629684150219,\"12\":0.0022428641095757484,\"13\":0.00135584175586